00:50:36,702 --> 00:50:39,130
I just followed her.

802
00:50:39,898 --> 00:50:42,639
She said she was spoken to.

803
00:50:42,882 --> 00:50:45,507
I think she's going to do something.

804
00:50:45,614 --> 00:50:48,601
What? Do what?

805
00:50:48,679 --> 00:50:52,844
My feet just lead me here.

806
00:50:56,913 --> 00:50:58,143
First...

807
00:51:00,431 --> 00:51:03,398
May I ask you to do me a favor?

808
00:51:04,538 --> 00:51:05,583
Well...

809
00:51:06,443 --> 00:51:08,610
What... what kind of...?

810
00:51:08,927 --> 00:51:11,498
Audrey Hepburn said this.

811
00:51:11,498 --> 00:51:14,052
'Everyone must be saved from pain.'

812
00:51:14,443 --> 00:51:17,985
'You must not abandon anyone!'

813
00:51:18,083 --> 00:51:19,340
Please!

814
00:51:19,701 --> 00:51:21,585
Please understand the desperation
a mom feels

815
00:51:21,585 --> 00:51:23,469
when she's looking for her lost son!

816
00:51:23,880 --> 00:51:27,963
We need your help and participation!

817
00:51:31,536 --> 00:51:37,322
<i>Has anyone...</i>

818
00:51:38,028 --> 00:51:43,748
<i>seen this person?</i>

819
00:51:43,967 --> 00:51:47,865
<i>His name is Son Se Yoon...</i>

820
00:51:47,865 --> 00:51:50,429
It's nice to volunteer.

821
00:51:50,429 --> 00:51:54,010
But we could look a bit
all over the place.

822
00:51:55,036 --> 00:51:58,639
We are doing this with a pure intention.

823
00:51:58,639 --> 00:52:02,449
There will be a lot of these things.
I hope you're not regretting.

824
00:52:07,400 --> 00:52:09,989
Hello. Please read this.

825
00:52:10,072 --> 00:52:13,364
What am I supposed to do?
Even Madam Oh is involved.

826
00:52:14,849 --> 00:52:18,581
Come quickly. I'm worried
what might happen.

827
00:52:28,847 --> 00:52:30,298
Where are you?

828
00:52:30,298 --> 00:52:33,487
She's doing exorcism so
she can find Mr. Son.

829
00:52:33,617 --> 00:52:34,829
Really?

830
00:52:34,829 --> 00:52:37,978
I heard she's a famous shaman
from Mia-ri.

831
00:52:43,365 --> 00:52:45,818
What's all this?

832
00:52:45,913 --> 00:52:48,048
How would I know?

833
00:52:48,233 --> 00:52:49,710
Gosh.

834
00:52:50,771 --> 00:52:53,646
This is such nonsense!

835
00:52:53,646 --> 00:52:55,527
Is this a show or what?

836
00:52:55,576 --> 00:52:59,313
Let's play a round!

837
00:53:13,610 --> 00:53:14,898
Oh, my!

838
00:53:21,922 --> 00:53:23,070
Why is she doing that?

839
00:53:23,070 --> 00:53:25,869
I don't know.
I guess a spirit is upon her.

840
00:53:32,423 --> 00:53:33,536
Honey.

841
00:53:34,159 --> 00:53:35,353
What's going on?

842
00:53:49,931 --> 00:53:52,327
My son has come!

843
00:53:53,465 --> 00:53:57,202
My son! My poor child!

844
00:53:57,659 --> 00:54:00,673
Come to your mom's arms!

845
00:54:01,181 --> 00:54:04,639
My poor child!

846
00:54:04,639 --> 00:54:09,483
Come to your mom's arms!
Come to my arms!

847
00:54:14,304 --> 00:54:16,443
Oh, Gi Bum!

848
00:54:16,443 --> 00:54:18,313
Gi Bum! What's wrong?

849
00:54:18,485 --> 00:54:19,688
Gi Bum!

850
00:54:20,797 --> 00:54:24,215
What's wrong?
What's wrong with you?

851
00:54:24,336 --> 00:54:26,226
Gi Bum! What's wrong?

852
00:54:53,233 --> 00:54:55,027
Are you Se Yoon?

853
00:54:55,358 --> 00:54:57,485
Yes, Mom.

854
00:54:57,661 --> 00:54:59,532
My poor child!

855
00:54:59,951 --> 00:55:02,443
Welcome back!

856
00:55:02,443 --> 00:55:05,682
Welcome back, my child!

857
00:55:05,682 --> 00:55:07,409
Mom!

858
00:55:07,409 --> 00:55:09,679
My child!

859
00:55:18,018 --> 00:55:19,605
What's wrong with him?

860
00:55:20,878 --> 00:55:22,222
Director Bong.

861
00:55:22,222 --> 00:55:23,389
Yes.

862
00:55:23,900 --> 00:55:26,099
It must be hard on you.

863
00:55:26,579 --> 00:55:28,378
Because of me...

864
00:55:28,416 --> 00:55:31,820
Not at all, Mr. Son.

865
00:55:33,536 --> 00:55:34,722
Producer Lee.

866
00:55:34,722 --> 00:55:36,028
Yeah?

867
00:55:51,199 --> 00:55:52,608
Mr. Yoon.

868
00:55:53,221 --> 00:55:55,373
Yeah?

869
00:56:01,873 --> 00:56:05,045
How could you... out of all...

870
00:56:06,329 --> 00:56:07,822
It's not a mistake...

871
00:56:07,822 --> 00:56:11,362
Wake up, Gi Bum! You aren't Mr. Son!

872
00:56:11,362 --> 00:56:14,112
Wake up! Wake up!

873
00:56:27,869 --> 00:56:29,891
My poor child.

874
00:56:31,032 --> 00:56:32,920
Who did this to you?

875
00:56:33,588 --> 00:56:34,983
Mom...

876
00:56:36,440 --> 00:56:38,072
It's one of them here.

877
00:56:38,985 --> 00:56:40,215
Who?

878
00:56:41,989 --> 00:56:45,085
That person is...

879
00:56:48,222 --> 00:56:49,989
That person is...

880
00:56:52,918 --> 00:56:54,817
That person is...

881
00:56:55,684 --> 00:56:56,909
What...

882
00:57:17,635 --> 00:57:23,351
I, Yoon Tae Soo, will take care
of Kim Eun Ok until my death.

883
00:57:23,427 --> 00:57:25,434
I don't need this.

884
00:57:25,536 --> 00:57:27,452
Don't you hate me?

885
00:57:29,005 --> 00:57:31,059
I'm like a worm.

886
00:57:31,536 --> 00:57:35,164
Go, just go.

887
00:57:35,650 --> 00:57:38,231
Go. Just go!

888
00:57:50,686 --> 00:57:53,840
Tae Soo! I'm so sorry!

889
00:57:53,840 --> 00:57:57,472
Tae Soo! I'm sorry!

890
00:57:58,318 --> 00:58:00,719
Tae Soo, come down!

891
00:58:01,369 --> 00:58:03,085
I am sorry!

892
00:58:03,197 --> 00:58:05,612
Please get down!

893
00:58:05,688 --> 00:58:07,838
I did wrong.

894
00:58:07,900 --> 00:58:12,139
Tae Soo! Tae Soo!

895
00:58:12,463 --> 00:58:15,621
Tae Soo, get down!

896
00:58:17,338 --> 00:58:18,889
Tae Soo!

897
00:58:28,161 --> 00:58:30,498
You are in here.

898
00:58:30,574 --> 00:58:33,268
You are in here.

899
00:58:34,146 --> 00:58:35,628
My child!

900
00:58:36,414 --> 00:58:38,657
Where are you now?

901
00:58:38,804 --> 00:58:41,809
Half way up Bong Gal Mountain.

902
00:58:41,809 --> 00:58:43,677
Where exactly?

903
00:58:43,677 --> 00:58:47,327
In the back of the pine tree forest.

904
00:58:47,443 --> 00:58:49,246
Bong Gal Mountain?

905
00:58:49,335 --> 00:58:50,704
Stay focused.

906
00:58:50,704 --> 00:58:52,003
Bong Gal Mountain!

907
00:58:52,070 --> 00:58:53,289
Don't worry.

908
00:58:53,289 --> 00:58:55,476
To Bong Gal Mountain!

909
00:59:31,264 --> 00:59:33,434
What do we do now?

910
00:59:33,485 --> 00:59:36,697
Don't lose your focus.
We sink or swim!

911
00:59:36,704 --> 00:59:38,704
Is he possessed or something?

912
00:59:38,704 --> 00:59:41,318
Cross! Do you have a cross or garlic?

913
00:59:41,318 --> 00:59:43,903
They are useless.
Just knock him out!

914
00:59:43,903 --> 00:59:45,052
Ah!

915
00:59:55,710 --> 00:59:59,739
It's here! Right here!

916
01:00:00,728 --> 01:00:01,817
Right here?

917
01:00:05,594 --> 01:00:06,675
Right here!

918
01:00:23,702 --> 01:00:25,094
Would it be true?

919
01:00:29,646 --> 01:00:32,889
Over here! There's something here!

920
01:00:34,467 --> 01:00:35,835
Something's in here.

921
01:00:35,835 --> 01:00:37,072
Take it out!

